You need the following software

    gnuchess 5.07 
    gtk 2.4
    mono-0.91
    gtk-sharp-0.91
    librsvg-2.6
    
Also note, that for book opening you need correct install of gnuchess book,
some distributions, for example, Fedora, doesn't do it correctly.

To run the game, execute followng steps:

1. Copy csboard directory anywhere you like, for example in /usr/share/csboard
2. Copy csboard file to your path and modify it according to csboard dir prefix.
3. Enjoy the game.